					<div class="bx">
						<div class="img"><A href="../2023/Company-News_0206/1.html" title="Small filling machinery brings new thinking and scientization"><img src="../uploadfile/2023/0206/20230206031229401.jpg" alt="Small filling machinery brings new thinking and scientization" /></A></div>
						<div class="txt">
							<h2><A href="../2023/Company-News_0206/1.html" title="Small filling machinery brings new thinking and scientization">Small filling machinery brings new thinking and scientization</A></h2>
